{"tid":671530,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"片載主任曾准許學生入內：浸大剪走再拒陳樂行上訴","createTime":"2018-05-20T08:13:59.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-23T02:12:51.000Z","uid":63183,"like":59,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"f713dc19669a1ba2b833d55472ea69d5d8305cc7","tid":671530,"uid":63183,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-20T08:13:59.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=9V4wImsFIgc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D9V4wImsFIgc&d=C29PdPJit049SSA3pMxrJtU7RO4jIL0fLOArxO5LqtQ%3D&h=2666aafc\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=9V4wImsFIgc</a><br />\n<br />\nHong Kong Baptist University 香港浸會大學 早前頒布判決書，忽然聲稱「學生無聽勸喻離開語文中心」。翻查 港語學 足本影片，不但無此紀錄，反而喺條片第7秒已經紀錄低語文中心主任李贏西曾准許學生入內嘅言論，居然咁都剪走。點解堂堂大學，可以無中生有，硬砌學生生豬肉？<br />\n<br />\n審訊期間，四段影片都經不具名職員剪輯，但都無法證實學生係「強闖語文中心」。剪接影片只呈現對被告不利之部分，對被告學生極不公平。但係，即使山神指出新證據，周偉立副校為首嘅學生委員會，仍然拒絕上訴，審都唔審，令人咋舌。<br />\n<br />\n浸大捩橫折曲，無非都係要為錢大康未審先判嘅「暫時停學令」說項。希望今次節錄俾市民睇清片段，不容錢大康抵賴。"},{"pid":"940058548421d2b70bc0add6447f8528c2217a55","tid":671530,"uid":63183,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-20T08:16:40.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/hkbumountaingod/videos/vb.1569129996710834/1907110936246070/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fhkbumountaingod%2Fvideos%2Fvb.1569129996710834%2F1907110936246070%2F&d=C29PdPJit049SSA3pMxrJtU7RO4jIL0fLOArxO5LqtQ%3D&h=30d5a809\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/hkbumountaingod/videos/vb.1569129996710834/1907110936246070/</a>"},{"pid":"4b662572496c0ce6a5a243cb75b16266d940bc30","tid":671530,"uid":66324,"like":0,"dislike":14,"score":-14,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-20T08:20:07.000Z","msg":"但可以點做?<br />\n鬧上法庭?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bb1f80c2144c86ef59b0e18eb3953ec781003e5a","tid":671530,"uid":63183,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"4b662572496c0ce6a5a243cb